**Problem description:**
We use this code to paint icon in form.
```
public partial class Form1 : Form
    {
        public Form1()
        {
            InitializeComponent();
        }

        private void Form1_Paint(object sender, PaintEventArgs e)
        {
            e.Graphics.DrawIcon(new Icon("Image.ico"), 0, 0);
        }
    }
```
When use .NET Core, image bit depth decreased. Is this design?
Would you like to share some workaround? Thanks a lot.

